				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Well, this is all fine and dandy, but let me tell you that pets are close to useless in Qvic and beyond. Pets simply evaporate due to the AoEs and AoE rampage in the high-level zones. 
<br />

<br />
Calliav and Prism Skin are woefully inadequate for high-end play where there are four or five active mobs in close proximity.
<br />

<br />
Yes, mage DPS is completely gimp due to pets designed for pre-elemental play (even with Jennu's boots). 
<br />

<br />
The class is dead unless this (and some other things) are changed. 
<br />

<br />
Mages are not a meaningful DPS class any more in GoD.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.sovereignguild.org/forum/viewtopic.php?t=4429" target="_blank" class="postlink">Sage Itchyban of Veeshan</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
